TylesBase Installation Instructions.
====================================

Let <tylesBase> refer to the source directory. 

1. Make sure the following prerequisites are installed:

   ocaml
   findlib
   ocamldsort
   extLib

2. Change to the <tylesBase> directory

   cd <tylesBase>

3. To compile, type

   make all

   This will generate the files tylesBase.cm* files under src/_build.

4. To make the documentation, type

   make doc

   This produces documentation in html format under doc/html.

5. If needed, you can delete all automatically generated files by
   typing
   
   make clean
